sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Validator
    participant Handler
    participant Domain as N8NConfiguration
    participant Encryption
    participant DB as Database
    participant Events

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/admin/workflows/n8n
    Note right of Client: {name, baseUrl, apiKey, webhookUrl}

    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Extract payload
    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Create CreateN8NConfigCommand

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(command)

    Mediator->>Validator: Validate(command)
    Validator->>Validator: Check baseUrl is valid HTTP/HTTPS
    Validator->>Validator: Check webhookUrl format
    Validator->>Validator: Verify admin role
    Validator->>Mediator: Validation passed ✓

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>DB: Check if active config exists
    DB-->>Handler: Existing active config found

    Handler->>Encryption: EncryptApiKey(apiKey)
    Encryption->>Encryption: AES-256 encryption
    Encryption-->>Handler: Encrypted key

    Handler->>Domain: N8NConfiguration.Create(name, baseUrl, encryptedKey, webhookUrl, userId)
    Domain->>Domain: Set IsActive = false (manual activation)
    Domain->>Domain: CreatedAt = UtcNow
    Domain->>Events: Raise N8NConfigurationCreatedEvent

    Handler->>DB: Deactivate previous config (if setting as active)
    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(configuration)
    DB-->>Handler: Configuration saved ✓

    Handler->>Events: Publish N8NConfigurationCreatedEvent

    Handler-->>Mediator: N8NConfigurationDto
    Note over Handler: API key masked in response

    Mediator-->>Endpoint: N8NConfigurationDto

    Endpoint-->>Client: 201 Created
    Note left of Client: {id, name, baseUrl, apiKey: "***"}
